{
  "texts": [
    "For each task category, a structured prompt included a set of 3 questions (in varied difficulties) and response formatting guidelines.",
    "Computational and Social Tasks were multiple choice tests while the Summarization Task was open-ended.",
    "\"No-Task\" involved no skill-based assessments before prompting with the GSES (no tasks given).",
    "The tasks and rubric for acceptable responses were selected from public datasets.",
    "[24] [25] [26] For the Summarization Task, the study team identified key components of an acceptable summary for each question."
  ]
}